flowRoot.flowPara: The Just Another Beep-Boop Machine is your opportunity to make some music. Using the supplied cards and hole punches, experiment by punching a for a long note, or for a short note.
To play a song, insert the rounded side of the card into the front of the machine. The motor will draw the card forward, and your song will play.

text.tspan: Punch a for a long note
Punch a for a short note
